to provide social protection for the informal sector workers.
</P>
<P>
Speaking at the opening of a three-day workshop on promoting
employment with gender equality in Zimbabwe in Nyanga of east
Zimbabwe, Moyo said there was need for various forms of protection
for this sector as the majority of labor force was moving into it.
</P>
