<HEADLINE> Mexican President-elect Visits Canada </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
OTTAWA, August 22 (Xinhua) -- Mexican President-elect Vicente
Fox arrived here Tuesday for a two-day visit, during which he will
push for stronger trade ties and more investment.
</P>
<P>
Fox is expected to meet Canadian Prime Minister Jean Chretien,
some cabinet ministers, Official Opposition leader Stockwell of
Canadian Alliance and Bloc Quebecois leader Gilles Duceppe.
</P>
