15 percent over the last six years, with Canada counting Mexico as
its ninth biggest trading partner.
</P>
<P>
Fox is also expected to ask Canada and the United States to
increase cash for a Mexico development fund established under
NAFTA.
</P>
<P>
He will meet the Business Council on National Issues to discuss
investment Wednesday, before going on with a visit to the United
States. 
