atmosphere of tolerance, of give-and-take, brotherliness and good
neighborliness, adding that the objectives would not be achieved
if everyone took up arms against each other.
</P>
<P>
"As a nation of diversity, tolerance and dialogue are the only
hope for survival," added the president. 
