August 12, 2000, its crew perished. Expressing my grief for the
perished and condolences to their families and relatives, I
announce August 23, 2000 a day of mourning in the Russian
Federation," Putin said in a decree released by the Kremlin press
service. (Russia-Kursk-Mourning)
