were challenged at the Lockerbie trial as it resumed on Tuesday
after a three-week summer recess.
</P>
<P>
The defense team asked the prosecution to provide cable
communications in their entity after it argued that the version
sent to the defense team had been edited with sections and words
blanked out. (Netherland-Lockerbie-Trial)
</P>
<P>
- - - -
</P>
<P>
NEW DELHI -- Visiting Maldives President Abdul Gayoom said here
