<TEXT>
<P>
NEW DELHI, August 22 (Xinhua) -- The Sensitive Index (Sensex)
continued to rise on the Bombay Stock Exchange (BSE) Tuesday due
to a frenzied buying by Foreign Institutional Investors (FIIs) as
well as speculators.
</P>
