which is the first of its kind in the country and will be held at
the Rizal Memorial Baseball Stadium in Manila, is a prelude to a
bigger tournament slated on August, 2001, the president said.
</P>
<P>
The said games, he added, aim to raise funds for the benefit of
underprivileged children who play the sport through the
establishment of educational scholarship programs. 
