international situation, China's diplomatic and defence policies,
and China's principled position on the Taiwan issue.
</P>
<P>
He also talked briefly about China's domestic situation and the
military building.
</P>
<P>
Lubasi said that he agrees with Xiong that the two countries
have been maintaining long-term friendly relations. He expressed
the hope that the two sides will further their relationship.
