<HEADLINE> Large Amount of Heroin Seized at Border </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
KUNMING, August 22 (Xinhua) -- Chinese border police have
seized 23.27 kg of refined heroin at Mukang border checkpoint in
southwest China's Yunnan Province recently.
</P>
