<HEADLINE> English Premier League Scorers </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LONDON, August 21 (Xinhua) -- Following are the scorers in the
English premier league after Monday's match:
</P>
<P>
2 - Mario Stanic (Chelsea), Alan Smith (Leeds), Alen Boksic (
Middlesbrough), Hassan Kachloul (Southampton)
</P>
